,"status_code":200},{"url":"https://httpbin.org/post","status":"delivered","timestamp":"2026-05-23T16:19:21.937154+00:00","event_type":"meeting.status_change","status_code":200}]},"segments":[{"start":3.594,"end":27.9,"text":"Hi Leo, this is Maya Chen starting case composed Kesa for Run Compose BVFR Zudk WJ 20,260,523 T155,551 Z. I will keep each turn short so we can test meeting intelligence without overlapping audio.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:57:18.861420","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:55:59.542000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:56:23.848000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:0"},{"start":23.328,"end":35.534,"text":"Thanks, Maya. This is Leo Santos. I will answer you directly and together we will test whether Vexa hears two named speakers in Google Meet.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:57:28.874122","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:56:19.276000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:56:31.482000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:0"},{"start":42.763,"end":55.81,"text":"First Checkpoint, a developer calls the API Gateway, asks for a bot to join and Vaxa handles browser control audio capture and cleanup.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:57:48.888783","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:56:38.711000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:56:51.758000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:1"},{"start":60.491,"end":71.538,"text":"I hear you. The second checkpoint is speaker labels. The listener transcript should separate Maya Chen from Leo Santos instead of mixing us together.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:57:58.902438","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:56:56.439000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:07.486000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:1"},{"start":81.253,"end":91.809,"text":"Spanish Checkpoint, buenos días, Leo. Vaxa convierte reuniones de Google Meet y Microsoft Teams en inteligencia de reuniones en tiempo real.","language":"es","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:58:18.912062","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:17.201000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:27.757000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:2"},{"start":97.957,"end":107.541,"text":"French Checkpoint. Bonjour Maya. Les webbooks doivent annoncer le statut de la réunion, les erreurs et la transcription finale.","language":"fr","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:58:38.924937","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:33.905000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:43.489000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:2"},{"start":112.514,"end":123.824,"text":"Nice. Back in English, a support team can use Vaxa to capture customer calls, action items, objections, and promised follow-ups.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:58:58.938037","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:48.462000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:57:59.772000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:3"},{"start":130.727,"end":139.54,"text":"Les webbooks doivent être en train de faire des transcripts, les erreurs et les écoles.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:59:09.532217","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:06.675000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:15.488000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:3"},{"start":147.385,"end":157.834,"text":"Português e Checkpoint. Olá, Léo. Infraestrutura CellFoster ajuda equipes a controlar logs, armazenamento e retencal de gravacores.","language":"pt","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:59:29.556368","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:23.333000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:33.782000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:4"},{"start":159.661,"end":169.552,"text":"Good handoff, Maya. The self-hosted point matters because teams want reliable logs and predictable data boundaries.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:59:39.561827","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:35.609000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:45.500000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:4"},{"start":175.337,"end":185.81,"text":"For scoring, I am responsible for meeting intelligence, the API Gateway, self-hosted deployment and the final takeaway.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T15:59:59.574204","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:58:51.285000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:01.758000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:5"},{"start":187.939,"end":197.556,"text":"For scoring, I am responsible for Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, speaker labels, webhooks and recordings.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:00:09.578590","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:03.887000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:13.504000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:5"},{"start":201.5,"end":213.838,"text":"Leo, please confirm the operations report should include bot lifecycle, first transcript time, webhook delivery and stop status.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:00:19.583689","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:17.448000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:29.786000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:6"},{"start":216.357,"end":227.57,"text":"The report should also mention whether the dashboard updated in real time and whether playback or transcript artifacts are available.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:00:39.595998","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:32.305000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:43.518000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:6"},{"start":233.576,"end":243.84,"text":"My final takeaway is that Vexa turns live meeting audio into programmable meeting intelligence for real products.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:00:49.606883","speaker":"Maya Chen-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:49.524000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T15:59:59.788000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-0:7"},{"start":247.875,"end":257.599,"text":"My final takeaway is that this named two-speaker demo should prove the listener heard Maya and Leo clearly. End of podcast.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:01:09.612294","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T16:00:03.823000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T16:00:13.547000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:7"},{"start":257.599,"end":269.523,"text":"End of podcast.","language":"en","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:01:19.621047","speaker":"Leo Santos-compose-case-a","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T16:00:13.547000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-05-23T16:00:25.471000Z","segment_id":"b821c09a-a76c-4b10-b21d-41d0e9e0dc9f:speaker-1:8"},{"start":1221.266,"end":1232.662,"text":"проверка раз два три 4 5 6 7 на регрессии этот real time работает хорошо","language":"ru","created_at":"2026-05-23T16:17:19.690289","speaker":"Dmitriy Grankin","completed":true,"absolute_start_time":"2026-05-23T16:16:17.214000Z","absolute_end_time":"2026-0